<font face=\"宋体\">日（周六</font>—周日）；前后周末正常休息，不调休。放假期间，紫薇门诊停诊，其余各院区门诊开展业余服务；节假日期间普通医技检查正常开展；发热门诊、急诊<font face=\"Times New Roman\">24</font><font face=\"宋体\">小时开放。各院区业余门诊具体开放科室安排如下：</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:26.0000pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><img src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/04/27/20220427085831571001.png\" border=\"0\"><br>\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:26.0000pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">放假期间门诊安排及出诊医师排班信息详询</font>66696879<font face=\"宋体\">（主院区）、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">88508990</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">（北院区）、</font>88358506<font face=\"宋体\">（五官科医院）、</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">66698899</font><font face=\"宋体\">（儿童医院）或登陆</font></span><span><a href=\"http://www.ycsyy.com/\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“盐城市第一人民医院”</span></a></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">门户网站</font>→“就医指南”→“门诊排班”→“节假日门诊安排”查询。假期门诊就诊接待请至各院区门诊一站式服务中心，具体安排以当天实际开诊为准。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:26.0000pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">感谢您选择在我院就诊！祝您身体健康，节日愉快！</font> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:26.0000pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:28.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:28.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 28pt; text-indent: 270pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;盐城市第一人民医院</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:21.0000pt;text-align:right;line-height:26.0000pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">二</font>○二</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">二</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">年四月二十</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">七</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">日</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:26.0000pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><br>\r\n</font></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2436','3259','1','','','因医院实际工作需要，于2022年4月28日进行招标的项目，经评标小组评审，中标结果如下：盐城市第一人民医院疫情防控指挥中心装修工程中标单位：江苏亮辉建设工程有限公司中标价：476748.86元为体现公开、公平、公正的原则，特此公告三天。如有疑问请与盐城市第一人民医院','10.10.20.14','10.10.20.14','1651225440','因医院实际工作需要，于2022年4月28日进行招标的项目，经评标小组评审，中标结果如下：<br>\r\n盐城市第一人民医院疫情防控指挥中心装修工程<br>\r\n中标单位：江苏亮辉建设工程有限公司<br>\r\n中标价：476748.86元<br>\r\n为体现公开、公平、公正的原则，特此公告三天。如有疑问请与盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室联系，电话0515-66696810。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 盐城市第一人民医院<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2022年4月29日','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2439','3262','1','','/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/04/29/20220429181122282001.png','各医疗设备生产企业、经营企业：为了满足医院诊疗工作的需要，经医院党委会研究决定，需对一批在用大中型医疗设备购买维保，服务年限3年。本批次项目将于近期开展市场调研和招标。欢迎符合条件的设备生产企业、经营企业前来参与。有意愿参与本次市场调研的设备生产企业','10.10.20.14','10.10.20.14','1651227170','<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">各医疗设备生产企业、经营企业：</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">为了满足医院诊疗工作的需要，经医院党委会研究决定，需对一批在用大中型医疗设备购买维保，服务年限3年。本批次项目将于近期开展市场调研和招标。欢迎符合条件的设备生产企业、经营企业前来参与。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"><img align=\"center\" border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/04/29/20220429181122282001.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">有意愿参与本次市场调研的设备生产企业、经营企业请于2022年05月 13日前将相关材料发送至邮箱：ycyysbc@qq.com。具体调研会时间另行通知。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">报名须知：</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">1.具有独立承担民事责任的能力。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">2.具有履行合同所必须具备的设备和专业知识。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">3.具有良好的商业信誉。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">4.近3年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">5.按要求填写《盐城市第一人民医院设备咨询报名表》（见附件）。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">6.报名截止时间：2022年05月13日24：00</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">联系人：李老师&nbsp; 联系方式：0515-88508946&nbsp; QQ:651830413(推荐)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/doc.gif\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/file/2022/04/29/20220429181246651.docx\">盐城市第一人民医院设备咨询报名表.docx</a></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2441','3264','1','','','《民法典》第七编第六章医疗损害责任第一千二百一十八条　患者在诊疗活动中受到损害，医疗机构或者其医务人员有过错的，由医疗机构承担赔偿责任。第一千二百一十九条　医务人员在诊疗活动中应当向患者说明病情和医疗措施。需要实施手术、特殊检查、特殊治疗的，医务人员','10.10.20.14','10.10.20.14','1652065129','<p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\ntext-align:center;line-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">《民法典》第七编第六章医疗损害责任</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百一十八条　患者在诊疗活动中受到损害，医疗机构或者其医务人员有过错的，由医疗机构承担赔偿责任。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百一十九条　医务人员在诊疗活动中应当向患者说</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">明</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">病情和医疗措施。需要实施手术、特殊检查、特殊治疗的，医务人员应当及时向患者具体说明医疗风险、替代医疗方案等情况，并取得其明确同意；不能或者不宜向患者说明的，应当向患者的近亲属说明，并取得其明确同意。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">医务人员未尽到前款义务，造成患者损害的，医疗机构应当承担赔偿责任。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十条　因抢救生命垂危的患者等紧急情况，不能取得患者或者其近亲属意见的，经医疗机构负责人或者授权的负责人批准，可以立即实施相应的医疗措施。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十一条　医务人员在诊疗活动中未尽到与当时的医疗水平相应的诊疗义务，造成患者损害的，医疗机构应当承担赔偿责任。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十二条　患者在诊疗活动中受到损害，有下列情形之一的，推定医疗机构有过错：</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">（一）违反法律、行政法规、规章以及其他有关诊疗规范的规定；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">（二）隐匿或者拒绝提供与纠纷有关的病历资料；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">（三）遗失、伪造、篡改或者违法销毁病历资料。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十三条　因药品、消毒产品、医疗器械的缺陷，或者输入不合格的血液造成患者损害的，患者可以向药品上市许可持有人、生产者、血液提供机构请求赔偿，也可以向医疗机构请求赔偿。患者向医疗机构请求赔偿的，医疗机构赔偿后，有权向负有责任的药品上市许可持有人、生产者、血液提供机构追偿。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十四条　患者在诊疗活动中受到损害，有下列情形之一的，医疗机构不承担赔偿责任：</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">（一）患者或者其近亲属不配合医疗机构进行符合诊疗规范的诊疗；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">（二）医务人员在抢救生命垂危的患者等紧急情况下已经尽到合理诊疗义务；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">（三）限于当时的医疗水平难以诊疗。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">前款第一项情形中，医疗机构或者其医务人员也有过错的，应当承担相应的赔偿责任。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十五条　医疗机构及其医务人员应当按照规定填写并妥善保管住院志、医嘱单、检验报告、手术及麻醉记录、病理资料、护理记录等病历资料。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">患者要求查阅、复制前款规定的病历资料的，医疗机构应当及时提供。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十六条　医疗机构及其医务人员应当对患者的隐私和个人信息保密。泄露患者的隐私和个人信息，或者未经患者同意公开其病历资料的，应当承担侵权责任。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十七条　医疗机构及其医务人员不得违反诊疗规范实施不必要的检查。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">第一千二百二十八条　医疗机构及其医务人员的合法权益受法律保护。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.4000pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;\r\nline-height:15.0500pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">干扰医疗秩序，妨碍医务人员工作、生活，侵害医务人员合法权益的，应当依法承担法律责任。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;font-size:14.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2442','3265','1','','','因医院实际工作需要，于2022年5月12日进行招标的项目，经评标委员会评审，中标结果如下：一、盐城市第一人民医院污水处理药剂采购项目中标单位：盐城市绿洲环保科技有限公司中标价：16.58万元二、盐城市第一人民医院主院区汽水热交换器维修项目中标单位：盐城傲博燃气有','10.10.20.14','10.10.20.14','1652405745','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">因医院实际工作需要，于</font>2022年</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">5</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">月</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">12</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">日</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">进行招标的项目，经评标</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">委员会</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">评审，中标结果如下：</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">一、</font></span></b><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院污水处理药剂采购项目</font></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">中标单位：盐城市绿洲环保科技有限公司</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">中标价：</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">16.58</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">万元</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">二、盐城市第一人民医院主院区汽水热交换器维修项目</font></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">中标单位：</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-weight:n